<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/valuation-tribunal-service-for-england-valuation-tribunal-service> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Valuation Tribunal Service (VTS) is an administrative statutory body. It supports the Valuation Tribunal for England in its work dealing with appeals about Council Tax and non-domestic (business) rates. VTS is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ."@en .
